To compile eBook-speaker, be sure the following extra packages are installed:

   libncurses5-dev
   libncursesw5-dev
   libsox-dev
   libmagic-dev
   libxml2-dev
   libidn11-dev

Give the following command:

   $ make          

run the script install.sh, as user root, to install eBook-speaker onto
your system:

   # ./install.sh
